<P>
   ALA-AUTO-ASSEMBLY (Detroit) _ DaimlerChrysler plans to announce
on Monday that it will nearly double production in Alabama, adding
another assembly line close to the site where it already builds
M-Class sport utility vehicles. By Keith Bradsher.
