<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DEFIANT-PRAYER0828-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Defiant prayers resound at games
 &HT;    By James Salzer
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
