<P>
   Here are tonight's columns and regular features:
</P>
<P>
   NEW-ECONOMY-COLUMN (Frankfurt, Germany) _ Gamesmanship in
Europe's wireless auctions indicates that the European Union's
efforts to create a level playing field in telecommunications have
not yet been completely successful. By Edmund L. Andrews.
</P>
